        "template--18864357179699__3f3a9079-0620-4c01-a81b-0d9a81f50909-16866101186e9ae39e-1": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Empowering You Is Our Passion",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "template--18864357179699__3f3a9079-0620-4c01-a81b-0d9a81f50909-16866101186e9ae39e-2": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>DIY doesn’t mean doing it alone. We’re here to help you create wedding flowers you love — with support, guidance, and absolutely zero intimidation.  Founded by Martha Stewart Top Floral Designer Alison Fleck, Bloom Culture was created in 2014 to make wedding flowers approachable, fun, and totally doable. Our goal is simple: to help you save money and feel proud of what you create.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "7912c590-3bc8-4f8f-a7cf-3cc4f16e82c3": {
          "type": "buttons",
          "settings": {
            "button_text": "Explore Our DIY Collections",
            "button_url": "shopify://collections/diy-collections",
            "button_type": "btn--primary",
