          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>MEET ALISON</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        },
        "template--18864357179699__0e0996ac-dfb5-4a26-a8d4-cb4955c30709-16832549863afe86ac-0": {
          "type": "heading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "I Care About Your Wedding.",
            "heading_font_size": "heading-large",
            "padding_bottom": 16,
            "heading_tag": "automatic"
          }
        },
        "template--18864357179699__0e0996ac-dfb5-4a26-a8d4-cb4955c30709-16832549863afe86ac-1": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>With more than 15 years as a floral designer and shop owner, I’ve helped couples create beautiful flowers at every budget — from shoestring celebrations to full-scale events. That experience taught me that you don’t need a huge budget or professional training to make something stunning; you just need the right guidance. <br/><br/>I built Bloom Culture to give you exactly that — a clear, supportive process that removes the stress and uncertainty, no matter your vision or price point. If you’re feeling overwhelmed, I’ve got you. Truly.</p>",
            "text_font_size": "body-medium",
            "padding_bottom": 16
          }
        }
      },
