            "text": "<p>We believe making your own wedding flowers should feel joyful and not confusing. That’s why we give you clear recipes, honest advice, and step-by-step support from the moment your flowers arrive. It’s not just about saving money (though you will). It’s about creating memories with your people, and feeling proud of what you carry down the aisle.</p>",
